{"tid":1426106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光復香港   時代抗命","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:50:52.000Z","uid":267763,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c832188b913b2bd5a03dc2ecc6558d47f3722673","tid":1426106,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:49:47.000Z","msg":"近日發現其實唔少人都對「時代革命」呢個口號有D意見。<br />\n<br />\n其實革命既重點系，<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">破舊立新</span></strong>，例如工業大革命就系人手被機器取替，吾一定系講緊推翻政府。<br />\n<br />\n不過既然革命會令社會各界聯想到推翻政權，咁我地倒不如將「革命」二字，改成「抗命」<br />\n<br />\n公民抗命系人人都有既意識，系市民透過和平手段（和平不代表合法，eg佔路，吾交稅等等）向政府表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得新口號應該系<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代抗命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3332443b54882fc1b461b6822ebf5bd5023dec97","tid":1426106,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:50:04.000Z","msg":"自推一次"},{"pid":"7bd9fe5e9d356939702e99fc8731c87742005976","tid":1426106,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:50:15.000Z","msg":"自推兩次"},{"pid":"ac86a71299c3f84df7c17387d3b59c7a604b6585","tid":1426106,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:50:28.000Z","msg":"自推三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df40d66781dc702ab99e91f208f434369510b682","tid":1426106,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:50:38.000Z","msg":"自推四次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a883e4a7677cf709b5113f1f975ab5f639d68e17","tid":1426106,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:50:52.000Z","msg":"自推五次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}